Why not?
为什么不？

288
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,320
Come on.
拜托。

289
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:20,360
Just a cute little puppy or kitty.
就一只可爱的小狗或小猫。

290
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:22,640
Who's going to look after a dog or a cat?
谁来照顾狗或猫？

291
