你喜欢雪貂、仓鼠这些好东西吗？

311
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:14,400
I don't like small pets.
我不喜欢小宠物。

312
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:15,800
I love big pets.
我喜欢大宠物。

313
00:12:15,800 --> 00:12:17,160
So as a kid we had both.
小时候我们两种都养过。

314
00:12:17,160 --> 00:12:20,720
My brother really loved small animals like hamsters and ferrets and things like that.
我哥哥真的很喜欢小动物，比如仓鼠、雪貂之类的。

315
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:22,120
I just think they're a little bit stinky.
我只是觉得它们有点臭。

316
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:24,280
They kind of smell funny.
它们闻起来怪怪的。

317
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:28,360
So ever since, I've always really liked big animals like dogs.
从那以后，我一直很喜欢像狗这样的大动物。

318
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,440
So you are a dog person.
所以你是个爱狗的人。

319
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,440
I am a dog person.
我是个爱狗的人。

320
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:33,240
This is something interesting that we describe in English.
这是我们在英语中描述的一个有趣现象。

321
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,920
People say I am a dog person.
人们说我是一个爱狗的人。

322
00:12:34,920 --> 00:12:36,520
I am a cat person.
我是一个爱猫的人。

323
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:39,120
It's almost like it says something about your personality.
这几乎像是在说你的性格。

324
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,120
Exactly.
没错。

325
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:43,600
So if you're a dog person, it means that you prefer dogs or you like dogs.
所以如果你是一个爱狗的人，意思是你更喜欢狗或喜欢狗。

326
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:46,240
If you're a cat person, you prefer cats.
如果你是一个爱猫的人，你更喜欢猫。

327
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:51,400
And a lot of people really like dogs but don't really like cats or they love cats and they
很多人真的很喜欢狗，但不太喜欢猫，或者他们爱猫却

328
00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:52,920
can't stand dogs.
受不了狗。

329
00:12:52,920 --> 00:12:53,920
Right.
对。

330
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:58,680
And it even gets to the point where I've heard that maybe on dates people will ask, so are
甚至到了我听说在约会时人们会问，那么你是

331
00:12:58,680 --> 00:13:00,480
you a dog person or a cat person?
爱狗的人还是爱猫的人？

332
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,720
I know that's how I pick dates.
我知道我就是这样挑选约会对象的。

333
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:02,720
Really?
真的吗？

334
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:03,720
What about you?
你呢？

335
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:04,720
Are you a dog person or a cat person?
你是爱狗的人还是爱猫的人？

336
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:07,120
I'm definitely a dog person.
我绝对是爱狗的人。

337
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,120
Good answer.
好答案。

338
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:09,120
Yeah.
嗯。

339
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:13,200
I think cats are, I mean they're nice and they're cuddly and I think they're very good
我觉得猫，它们很可爱，也很抱抱，而且我认为它们是很好的

340
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:18,200
indoor pets and a little bit more fun than maybe a hamster.
室内宠物，比仓鼠稍微有趣一点。

341
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:21,400
But I think dogs have more life and are more energetic.
但我认为狗更有活力，更有精力。

342
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:22,700
I think cats are very lazy.
我觉得猫很懒。

343
00:13:22,700 --> 00:13:25,800
And I think sometimes cats like to play mind games.
而且我觉得有时候猫喜欢玩心理游戏。

344
